OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774980701
OL,3,CArmed police in massage parlour stand-
OL,4,Coff with suspect
OL,6,FPolice have issued new details on a
OL,7,Fserious stand-off in a massage parlour
OL,8,Fin Radcliffe today. Armed police
OL,9,Fsealed off a street in the town in
OL,10,FBury with multiple police vehicles,
OL,11,Fincluding vans and undercover cars, at
OL,12,FStand Lane in Radcliffe.
OL,14,FArmed officers were pictured pointing
OL,15,Fguns towards a building, with images
OL,16,Fshowing the street cordoned off in
OL,17,Fboth directions with officers
OL,18,Fappearing to be stationed close to a
OL,19,Fnearby business.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
