PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774980701
OL,3,CArmed police in massage parlour stand-
OL,4,Coff with suspect
OL,6,FIn a statement Greater Manchester
OL,7,FPolice said "We are responding to an
OL,8,Fincident on Stand Lane, Radcliffe
OL,9,Ffollowing reports of a disturbance at
OL,10,Faround 2:15pm today (30/03/2026).
OL,12,FIt was reported that threats were
OL,13,Fbeing made at an address and the
OL,14,Fsuspect is believed to have been in
OL,15,Fpossession of a bladed weapon.
OL,17,FThankfully, those at the property
OL,18,Fmanaged to get a place of safety and
OL,19,Fno injuries have been reported.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774980701
OL,3,CArmed police in massage parlour stand-
OL,4,Coff with suspect
OL,6,FNo arrests have been made and our
OL,7,Fofficers are on scene to manage any
OL,8,Fpotential risk.
OL,10,FWe would like to reassure the public
OL,11,Fthat we believe this is an isolated
OL,12,Fincident and is not being treated as
OL,13,Fcounter terrorism related.
OL,15,FEnquiries are ongoing at this time"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
