PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774980701
OL,3,CArmed police in massage parlour stand-
OL,4,Coff with suspect
OL,6,FCounter Terrorist Specialist Firearms
OL,7,FOfficers (CTFO) were also been
OL,8,Fpictured in attendance on Stand Lane
OL,9,Fthis afternoon. GMP later confirmed
OL,10,Fthe incident was not being treated as
OL,11,Fcounter terrorism related.
OL,13,FTraffic is building in the area
OL,14,Fincluding on nearby New Road due to
OL,15,Fthe ongoing closure. Local bus
OL,16,Fservices have also been diverted this
OL,17,Fafternoon and Bury Council have warned
OL,18,Fpeople to 'avoid the area'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
